api_list.description: This resource returns information about League seasons.

required_parameters.name: endpoint
required_parameters.description: For the season ids of season 1-4, there will be an option to examine the legendary or guild endpoints. The guild endpoint will return the guild leaderboard, whereas the legendary will return the solo leaderboard. For the season id of season 5, the endpoints legendary or guild are not available, replaced instead with ladder.

optional_parameters.description: Valid languages are en, es, de, fr, ko and zh. If no language parameter is set, the language defaults to en.
